when you keep your cards hidden.

335
00:21:25.017 --> 00:21:28.487  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
But I thought you didn't need him anymore.
Isn't that right?

336
00:21:30.856 --> 00:21:34.059  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I just figured
it wasn't a winning hand anymore.

337
00:21:37.362 --> 00:21:40.499  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Also, don't eat this crap
when you're trying to lose weight.

338
00:21:42.868 --> 00:21:44.369  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What a jerk.

339
00:21:48.407 --> 00:21:49.675  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Nagai] <i>Juvenile hall, huh?</i>

340
00:21:51.610 --> 00:21:53.445  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>I guess I screwed Kai over pretty bad.</i>

341
00:21:54.813 --> 00:21:58.016  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>But... when I think of</i>
<i>what we'll be doing...</i>

342
