<i>that may be the safest place for him.</i>

343
00:22:19.104 --> 00:22:21.073  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gate opens, then closes]

344
00:22:21.340 --> 00:22:23.342  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
